1480
02:46:09,599 --> 02:46:10,825
Adik ipar.

1481
02:46:22,920 --> 02:46:24,850
Kau Lajjo?

1482
02:46:25,319 --> 02:46:27,247
Tunjukkan tanda pengenal.

1483
02:46:39,671 --> 02:46:42,061
