1488
02:46:54,157 --> 02:46:56,885
Bagaimana?

1489
02:46:56,887 --> 02:47:01,175
Disini tak ada mayat.

1490
02:47:03,880 --> 02:47:06,507
Kau lihat gadis itu?

1491
